  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a tagine pot over medium heat and drizzle with sesame oil.",
    "Place sliced mushrooms and halved potatoes into the pot, coating them evenly with oil and seasoning.",
    "Add sliced chillies, grated ginger, garlic powder, soy sauce, mirin, miso paste, and sugar to the pot.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth, stir well, and bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Cover the pot, let the mixture simmer for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Uncover, reduce heat to low, and bake uncovered for 10 more minutes until the top is crisp.",
    "Sprinkle toasted sesame seeds over the surface and let rest for 3 minutes.",
    "Garnish with chopped scallions before serving."
  ],
